    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I recognize there might be an edge case where automatically setting `--froms` to the account address may be breaking, so I was thinking a workaround might be getting the account address with `cast`. However, `--froms $(cast wallet address --account <ACCOUNT>)` asks for the password twice.\r\n\r\nPerhaps we can have a single `--fromAccount` that fills both `--account` and `--froms $(cast wallet address --account <ACCOUNT>)` using a single password?",
